Jerry Zaks Goes to Jujamcyn: Tony Award-winning director Jerry Zaks has 
resigned as director in residence at the Lincoln Center Theater, and will join 
Jujamcyn Theaters Sept. 15 in a salaried, untitled position that will allow him 
to develop plays and musicals for the company's five Broadway theaters. 
Officials said it is believed to be the first time that a theater owning and 
