ARMED FORCES; CHURCHES -- LIBERIA; LIBERIA -- REVOLTS; GUERRILLAS -- LIBERIA; 
LIBERIA -- GOVERNMENT; DOE, SAMUEL K 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
