<HEADLINE>
<P>
REGIONAL EARNINGS: TEKELEC DOUBLES ITS 2ND-QUARTER EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Tekelec, a Calabasas producer of communications testing equipment, said its 
second-quarter earnings more than doubled from a year earlier on an 18% 
increase in revenue. 
</P>
<P>
In the quarter that ended June 30, Tekelec's net income rose to $1.19 million 
from $563,000, while its revenue rose to $9.74 million from $8.25 million. The 
gains partly reflected strong international orders, which rose 38% in the 
quarter from a year earlier, Tekelec said. 
</P>
<P>
For the first half of 1990, Tekelec's profit rose to $2.38 million from $1.81 
million, and its six-month revenue increased 12% to $19.4 million from $17.4 
million. 
</P>
</TEXT>
