<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY FOCUS: NEWPORT BEACH; 
</P>
<P>
CENTER MAKES VAN AVAILABLE TO SENIORS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A van equipped with a wheelchair lift is available to senior citizens through 
the Oasis Senior Center. 
</P>
<P>
The van is offered for medical appointments, grocery shopping and rides to the 
Oasis center. A $1 donation is requested per one-way ride, and reservations 
should be made at least two days in advance, center officials said. 
Grocery-shopping trips will be made on a pre-scheduled group basis. 
</P>
<P>
For more information, call the Oasis Senior Center at (714) 644-3244. 
</P>
</TEXT>
