<DATE>
<P>
July 31, 1990, Tuesday, P.M. Final 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part P; Page 12; Column 1; Late Final Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Cry From Kashmir: Supporters of militant Jammu Kashmir Liberation Front 
