<TEXT>
<P>
Leslie's Poolmart -- Due to a wire service error, an item on Tuesday 
incorrectly said Richard H. Hillman is president of Leslie's Poolmart. 
</P>
<P>
Hillman is no longer president. He is a consultant and director for the 
Chatsworth company. Brian P. McDermott is the company's president. 
</P>
